<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,100;0,200;0">

    <title>Order Confirmation</title>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #4f5ef1;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .message {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-top: 50px;
        }

        .course-info {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px 2px rgba(206, 197, 197, 0.1);
            color: #000;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .course-info h4 {
            color: #23bd70;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .table th,
        .table td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .table th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 100px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .footer p a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="message">
            <h1>Your ELearning order is Confirmed!</h1>
            <p>And we're just as excited as you are.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="course-info">
            <h4>Here's what you ordered:</h4>
            <table style="border-bottom: 1px solid #0000002f;">
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        Order #: <%= order._id %>
                    </td>

                    <td>
                        Order Date #: <%= order.date %>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <table class="table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Item</th>
                        <th>Qty</th>
                        <th>Cost</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td><%= order.name %></td>
                        <td>1</td>
                        <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <table class="table">
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td>Total: $<%= order.price %></td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@amir.com">support@amir.com</a></p>
        </div>

        <p>&copy;2023 Elearning. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
